title: The Plimsouls - Kool Trash (1998) 320k MP3
description:
If you dig the Plimsouls, this is a must-have album. Made in 1998, Pete Case reunited with guitarist Eddie Munoz and bassist Dave Pahoa, and recruited drummer Clem Burke (from Blondie!) to keep the beat.  These are great songs, and if you're a Plimsouls fan, this record is a rarity, and a real treat.

I ripped this directly from the CD (bought it myself from their old http://www.lather.com/plimsouls/ website, which is no longer active) to 320k MP3, VBR.  It's pretty high quality, and great for an iPod.
